Hi everyone;
  Please excuse my improper typing,typo errors,sentences running long,etc....
I just bought:Fatal Frame 1,2 and 3 on PS 2 game discs. I have played similiar games such as:Haunting Ground and Rule of Rose...I just started the 1st game in this series:Fatal frame,so far evrything is going great. No freezing,no glitches,as of yet. I will be back with a fuller,better review when I am finished this game. From what I seen written,pretty much matches,on describing this game! Another spooky,adventure game.see ya's soon!
